query:
SELECT
                    c.character_id,
                    c.character_name,
                    c.corporation_id,
                    c.corporation_name,
                    c.alliance_id,
                    c.alliance_name
                FROM jwt_refresh_token jrt
                JOIN character c ON jrt.character_id = c.character_id
                WHERE token_hash = $1
                AND jrt.character_id = $2
